 range $\\gtrsim\\!140\\,\\text{eV}$ for\nelectrons and $\\gtrsim\\!70\\,\\text{keV}$ for protons exceeds the expected\n$\\sim\\!1\\%$ and nears equipartition ($>\\!0.1$) for the Wind events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Feb 2022 17:01:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-06"}
